<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Reply Notification</title>
    <style>
        /* Base Styles */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        h1, p {
            margin: 0;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #fefefe;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            color: #0070f3;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Wrapper */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
        }

        /* Button Style */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .email-footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 16px;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>New Reply to Your Question</h1>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video <strong>"<%= title %>"</strong>.</p>
            <p>Please log in to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion.</p>
            
            
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="mailto:support@brightyears.com">contact support</a>.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2025 Bright Years. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
